Sometime on a cool day during the past summer my dog rocked an 11 mile run with my boyfriend.
He told me and I was shocked, especially after hearing how quickly she bounced back after running it.
It was at this point when I realized that my dog *could* finish a half marathon if the conditions were right.

I have friends who have ran half marathons with their dog and heard stories of dogs even [joining in to half marathon distances](https://www.runnersworld.com/running-with-dogs/hound-bandits-half-marathon-in-alabama).
