We started at the very back of the 2nd wave to stay out of other runners way and make sure that Viira started slow.
I didn‚Äôt want her to burn out part way through the run so we were running at a slower pace than she was used to.
My tentative goal for her was between 2:10-2:15 but that was very flexible depending on how she was doing.
